name: baby organic So Hum Onesie
description:
Hummingbirds string together the mantra, So Hum. I am you...you are me. This baby blue onesie is adourned with black print with this sanksrit mantra that instills the philosophy that we are all part of all life and everything that surrounds us.

Mamas and mamas to be can identify with this in a very intimate way.

The "Yum" babybe bib is a lovely addition to this onesie.

Sizes available; 3-6 months, 6-12 months, and 12-18 months.
Please indicate in your note to seller the size desired.
